Installing File-&file-version;



The File package contains a utility for determining the type of files.

&buildtime; &file-time;
&diskspace; &file-compsize;

&aa-file-down;
&aa-file-dep;

 
 


Installation of File


Prepare File for compilation:

./configure --prefix=/usr 


Compile the package:

make


And install it:

make install



